About
.entry-header
About 1075 RV Resort
1075 RV Resort in Lake City, FL is a premier destination for RV enthusiasts and outdoor lovers. Located in the scenic surroundings of Lake City, this resort offers top-notch amenities and a wide range of activities for guests to enjoy. Whether you’re looking to relax by the pool, explore nature trails, or socialize with other RVers, 1075 RV Resort has something for everyone. With spacious RV sites, modern facilities, and friendly staff, this resort provides a comfortable and enjoyable experience for all visitors. Escape to the beauty of Lake City and create unforgettable memories at 1075 RV Resort.
Campground Rules
Camping is only allowed in designated campsites
Campsite occupancy is limited to six people per site
First-come campgrounds usually fill by early morning: plan ahead to obtain a site
Drinking water is normally available in all campgrounds
Campground Park Map
Frequently Asked Questions
Where is the nearest grocery store?
There is a Harvey’s Supermarket .4 miles away
Where is the nearest super center
Walmart Supercenter is 2.5 miles away
Are pets allowed?
Yes.
Can we have campfires at our camp sites?
Fire pits are available throughout the park
How far to State Parks
Itchetucknee Springs State Park is 20.4 miles away
Stephen Foster Folk Culture Center is 15.6  miles away
O’Leno State Park is 22.5 miles away
Big Shoals State Park is 21.2 miles away
Osceola National Forest is 16.6 miles away
